<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Scheduled publication time</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">You only need to put in a scheduled publication time for the removal of a message, not for the addition.

</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Collection page</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">Make sure you add the new document to the <a href="https://signon.publishing.service.gov.uk/users/sign_in" class="govuk-link">HMRC service availability and issues</a> document collection. Do not create a public change note.
</p>